summary: A savegame pack which includes 6 different characters. They all do start at level 1 or 2, at the first Village. Have fun :)
descriptionHtml:
I didnt intend to create some kind of \"supermodels\". I tried to keep them near to the fantasy lore, plus adding some of my personal taste.
I cant remember which mod exactly i used, so forgive me if your characters might look different than shown in the pics, but im sure you can guess which kind of mods are included.

So we have:

- Iorveth, the wood elf

- Shani, the breton

- Sharifa, the redguard

- Tarrok, the orc

- Thorgal, the nord

- Ves, the dark elf

They all start at the first village at level 1 or 2. Have fun :)
author: Chaos Chief
